  {
    question: "What makes your school different from others?",
    answer: "Our school combines academic excellence with innovative technology integration, creative arts programs, and a strong focus on community building. We provide personalized learning experiences that help each student reach their full potential."
  },
  {
    question: "What technology programs do you offer?",
    answer: "We offer comprehensive technology education including computer science, robotics, digital media, and coding classes. Our students have access to modern computer labs, 3D printers, and the latest educational software."
  },
  {
    question: "How do you support students with different learning styles?",
    answer: "We believe every child learns differently. Our teachers use various teaching methods including visual, auditory, and kinesthetic approaches. We also provide additional support through our learning resource center."
  },
  {
    question: "What extracurricular activities are available?",
    answer: "We offer a wide range of activities including sports teams, music ensembles, drama club, art classes, robotics club, and various academic competitions. Students can explore their interests and develop new skills."
  },
  {
    question: "How do you ensure student safety?",
    answer: "Student safety is our top priority. We have comprehensive security measures, trained staff, and regular safety drills. Our campus is monitored and we maintain strict visitor policies."
  },
  {
